 *   maintained by `CombatSystem`. Wire the two together.
 * - @ref tutorial_spatial_world — AI aggro scans use
 *   `SpatialIndex::QueryRadius` to find nearby targets.
 * - @ref tutorial_game_objects — `AIBrain` lives on game
 *   objects; Transform and Movement drive the NPC's actual
 *   motion once the tree decides where to go.
 * - `include/cgs/game/behavior_tree.hpp` — authoritative BT API.
 * - `include/cgs/game/ai_components.hpp` — `AIBrain` structure.
 * - `include/cgs/game/ai_types.hpp` — `AIState`, `BTStatus`,
 *   and tuning constants.
 */
